<div class="marquee-banner" role="marquee" aria-label="Announcements" tabindex="0">
  <div class="marquee-content">
    <span>☕️ FRESHLY BREWED ARTISANAL COFFEE</span>
    <span>🎂 HEAVENLY HOME-MADE CAKES</span>
    <span>✨ CRAFTED WITH LOVE</span>
    <span>🥐 DELICIOUS SAVORY BITES</span>
